Manning testified on Thursday that he had been forced to sleep naked the previous night, because he would have tried to prove to an officer that he was not a danger to himself.
Manning would have told the officer that he could have used the elastic of his slip or his tongs to hurt himself, but that he had not done so.
That night, Manning testified that his underwear, his tongs, and his glasses had been removed from his cell.
